Having Dan onboard and letting him loose on the tools at our disposal is a =
multiplier =E2=80=93 we should be able to add more value to portfolio compa=
nies without needing to build out a platform team.=C2=A0
Having him onboard also means that we can bring on more people without slow=
ing down.=C2=A0
Hiring Research Analysts=C2=A0
To that end, we=E2=80=99re opening up two roles I=E2=80=99ve been dreaming =
about for a while:=C2=A0
Atoms Research Analyst=C2=A0
Bits Research Analyst
When Not Boring is at its best, we=E2=80=99re explaining and investing in n=
ew things that push the limits of what=E2=80=99s possible.=C2=A0
Writing about a SaaS company can be interesting, but there are a lot of peo=
ple who do it better than I can. Explaining DAOs [ https://email.mg2.substa=
ck.com/c/eJxFkNuKgzAQhp-muatkcqq5yMXC0teQmIwaqonEuOLbb1phF-YAc_qZz9mCY8qnWd=
